{"id":"abagtha","term":"Abagtha","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>One of the seven eunuchs in Ahasuerus’s court (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Esther 1:10\">Esther 1:10</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Esther 2:21\">2:21</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Esther 1:10","Esther 2:21"]}